  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carl Hart, a mild-mannered alcoholic handyman, finds himself trapped in a time loop after finding his dear daughter murdered. Trapped within his house and stalked by a mysterious figure, Carl is in a race to find a way out of the loop or die over and over to a scandalous police officer. With enough evidence gathered, he might just avenge his daughter and go free, or he might just go mad.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399300/extras/d4c4dbf13140d1fc6dece8975fc61a86.poster.avif?t=1739169684\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399300/extras/d4c4dbf13140d1fc6dece8975fc61a86.webm?t=1739169684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sneak through your house and dodge your stalker's rage.  </i><i><br>  <br> <br>Find secrets hidden throughout the house by your dearly departed family.<br>  <br>Survive alone as your own house becomes your worst nightmare.<br>  <br>Document evidence through time to save yourself from a cruel fate.<br>  <br>Master your memory to solve over 20 puzzle variations.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the Murder of your beloved daughter.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399300/extras/285025bbcc477107ebd23d51a0e7b3dc.poster.avif?t=1739169684\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399300/extras/285025bbcc477107ebd23d51a0e7b3dc.webm?t=1739169684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carl Hart, a mild-mannered alcoholic handyman, finds himself trapped in a time loop after finding his dear daughter murdered. Trapped within his house and stalked by a mysterious figure, Carl is in a race to find a way out of the loop or die over and over to a scandalous police officer. With enough evidence gathered, he might just avenge his daughter and go free, or he might just go mad.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399300/extras/d4c4dbf13140d1fc6dece8975fc61a86.poster.avif?t=1739169684\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399300/extras/d4c4dbf13140d1fc6dece8975fc61a86.webm?t=1739169684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sneak through your house and dodge your stalker's rage.  </i><i><br>  <br> <br>Find secrets hidden throughout the house by your dearly departed family.<br>  <br>Survive alone as your own house becomes your worst nightmare.<br>  <br>Document evidence through time to save yourself from a cruel fate.<br>  <br>Master your memory to solve over 20 puzzle variations.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the Murder of your beloved daughter.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399300/extras/285025bbcc477107ebd23d51a0e7b3dc.poster.avif?t=1739169684\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399300/extras/285025bbcc477107ebd23d51a0e7b3dc.webm?t=1739169684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
